{"_id":"0CbiDgWueZ5YJixi","name":"Wild Wickhead","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"follower","data":{"abilities":{"agility":{"score":0},"presence":{"score":0},"strength":{"score":0},"toughness":{"score":0}},"hp":{"current":10,"max":10},"description":"<p>Wickheads are solitary by nature, but the wildest and vilest are cast even from that loose community. Wandering forests and rambling ruins, they take any company they can find. Fickle, suspicious and bad, you would be well-advised to keep them chained.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Trait: (d4)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.Grumpy&nbsp;</li>\n<li>2.Apathetic&nbsp;</li>\n<li>3.Careless&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.Moody</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Speciality: (d4)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1-2.Walking lightsource</li>\n<li>3.Expert with a knife (d4+2)&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.Backstab (test DR8 with d20 rolled by the GM. Deals weapon damage+3)&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Aside from their specialty they will carry up to five items.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Values: (d6)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.Holding long monologues about oneself&nbsp;</li>\n<li>2.Verbal conflicts within the group&nbsp;</li>\n<li>3.Getting paid in sharp weapons&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.Burnt meat&nbsp;</li>\n<li>5.Depressing stories&nbsp;</li>\n<li>6.Captured slaves</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","morale":7,"speciality":"","trait":"","value":""},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/wildwickhead.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Wild Wickhead","displayName":0,"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/wildwickhead.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"0CbiDgWueZ5YJixi","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
