{"_id":"WUjqrhQ5NGrOQ6ur","name":"Prowler","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"follower","data":{"abilities":{"agility":{"score":0},"presence":{"score":0},"strength":{"score":0},"toughness":{"score":0}},"hp":{"current":1,"max":1},"description":"<p>Lawless good-for-nothing crooks banished from civilization. Low on resources, allies and basic decency they seek retribution ... and coin.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Trait: (d4)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.Lazy&nbsp;</li>\n<li>2.Bragging&nbsp;</li>\n<li>3.Liar&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.Traitor</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Speciality: (d4)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.Disarm traps (you need to find them first)&nbsp;</li>\n<li>2.Steal single items&nbsp;</li>\n<li>3.Climb impossible routes alone&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.Finds trails and corners that keep the group hidden.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Values: (d6)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1. Payment in silver&nbsp;</li>\n<li>2. Food&nbsp;</li>\n<li>3. Gossip&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4. Liquor&nbsp;</li>\n<li>5.Pointless death&nbsp;</li>\n<li>6.Getting the credit for exploits</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","morale":7,"speciality":"","trait":"","value":""},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/prowler.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Prowler","displayName":0,"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/prowler.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"WUjqrhQ5NGrOQ6ur","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
