{"_id":"dGU2KHOqP8a6c27w","name":"Earthbound","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"follower","data":{"abilities":{"agility":{"score":0},"presence":{"score":0},"strength":{"score":0},"toughness":{"score":0}},"hp":{"current":8,"max":8},"description":"<p>These freaks are roughly three parts human to one part dog. Society sees them as foul, diseased and disloyal for a carrier of canine blood. Isolation and contempt have made them self-reliant scavengers.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Trait: (d4)</p>\n<p>1. Arrogant</p>\n<p>2. Quiet</p>\n<p>3. Joking</p>\n<p>4. Hypochondriac</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Speciality: (d4)</p>\n<p>1. Excellent cooking (d4 extra HP when resting)</p>\n<p>2. Finds the right path</p>\n<p>3. Senses danger</p>\n<p>4. Makes/repairs items</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Values: (d6)</p>\n<p>1. Fireplace discussions</p>\n<p>2. Praise</p>\n<p>3. Endless tasks</p>\n<p>4. Items as payment</p>\n<p>5. Carnal relations</p>\n<p>6. Diluted black poison</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","morale":7,"speciality":"","trait":"","value":""},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/earthbound.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Earthbound","displayName":0,"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/earthbound.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"dGU2KHOqP8a6c27w","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
{"_id":"ktJvvdHontt4txWG","name":"Pale One","permission":{"default":0,"rJEU6XERAWNvCOnp":3},"type":"follower","data":{"abilities":{"agility":{"score":0},"presence":{"score":0},"strength":{"score":0},"toughness":{"score":0}},"hp":{"current":5,"max":5},"description":"<p>As if fallen from the stars the pale ones fit in nowhere. This unwilling alienation makes them destructive and detached.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Trait: (d4)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.Bitter&nbsp;</li>\n<li>2.Incoherent</li>\n<li>3.Mute&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.Self-harming behaviour</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Speciality: (d4), once per day</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.Create d2 doses of a random decoction (see the class Occult Herbmaster)</li>\n<li>2.Create d2 doses Elixir Vitalis (heals d6 HP and stops infection)</li>\n<li>3.Use one random unclean Power&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.Use one random sacred Power</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Values: (d6)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>1.Not having to use their speciality all the time&nbsp;</li>\n<li>2.Cleanliness</li>\n<li>3.Listening to melancholic melodies&nbsp;</li>\n<li>4.A couple of hours alone in darkness&nbsp;</li>\n<li>5.Wine</li>\n<li>6.Obscure rituals with the group</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>","morale":7,"speciality":"","trait":"","value":""},"sort":100001,"flags":{},"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/paleone.png","token":{"flags":{},"name":"Pale One","displayName":0,"img":"systems/morkborg/icons/followers/paleone.png","tint":null,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"dimLight":0,"brightLight":0,"sightAngle":360,"lightAngle":360,"lightAlpha":1,"lightAnimation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5},"actorId":"ktJvvdHontt4txWG","actorLink":false,"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{},"bar2":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[],"effects":[]}
